1. Purpose

BAD-01 defines the complete backend architecture for People's Priorities AI.

It specifies:

API architecture
Service boundaries
Repository pattern
Firestore collections
Firebase Storage layout
Validation
Logging
Error handling
AI integration points
Future scalability

This document is the single source of truth for backend development.

2. Backend Principles

We will follow these principles throughout the project:

Thin Controllers
Business Logic in Services
Data Access through Repositories
Shared Schemas
Stateless APIs
Structured Logging
Idempotent Operations where possible
Versioned APIs
