5. API Versioning

Every endpoint begins with:

/api/v1/

Example:

POST /api/v1/submissions

Never expose unversioned APIs.

6. Standard Response Format
Success
{
  "success": true,
  "requestId": "...",
  "data": {},
  "message": "Submission accepted"
}
Error
{
  "success": false,
  "requestId": "...",
  "error": {
    "code": "VALIDATION_ERROR",
    "message": "...",
    "details": []
  }
}

Every response includes a requestId.

