🔷 Two Recommendations 

These are the only additions I'd make to BAD-01 because they'll pay off immediately:

1. Add OpenAPI as a First-Class Deliverable

FastAPI generates OpenAPI automatically. Treat it as part of the architecture.

Document:

/docs      → Swagger UI
/redoc     → ReDoc
/openapi.json

Every new endpoint must appear correctly in the generated API documentation.

2. Define Firestore Status Lifecycle Now

Rather than storing a generic status string, standardize it from the beginning:

DRAFT
    ↓
RECEIVED
    ↓
PROCESSING_AI
    ↓
REVIEW_READY
    ↓
RESOLVED